<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="137">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="137">Inflation (cur)</strong> field, select the conversion index for the transaction currency.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="138">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="138">Inflation (MST)</strong> field, select the conversion index for the accounting currency.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="139">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="139">Inflation (sec)</strong> field, select the conversion index for the reporting currency.</li>
