</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="141"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="141"><strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="141">Use exchange rates</strong> – If you select this option, on the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="141">Indexes and amounts</strong> FastTab, define the rules for using exchange rates to determine the transaction amounts (in the transaction currency, default currency, and secondary currency) for the target company:</p>
<ul sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="143">
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="143"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="143">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="143">Amount (cur)</strong> field, select the rule for converting the transaction amount into the transaction currency.</p>
