<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="144"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="144">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="144">Amount (MST)</strong> field, select the rule for converting the transaction amount into the accounting currency.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="145"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="145">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="145">Amount (sec)</strong> field, select the rule for converting the transaction amount into the reporting currency.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="146"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="146">In these three <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="146">Amount...</strong> fields, you can select the following rules:</p>
<ul sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="148">
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="148"><strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="148">From transaction currency</strong> – The amount is calculated from the amount of the source transaction through conversion at the exchange rate of the target company.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="149"><strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="149">Zero</strong> – The value <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="149">0</strong> (zero) is substituted.</li>
