</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="155"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="155">Select <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="155">Save</strong>, and then close the page.</p>
