<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="318">Go to <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="318">General ledger</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="318">Periodic tasks</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="318">Translation sessions</strong>.</li>
