<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="320">Select <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="320">Translation wizard</strong> to open the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="320">Translation</strong> wizard.</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="321">On the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="321">Welcome</strong> page, select <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="321">Next</strong>.</li>
</ol>
<p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="323"><img src="media/welcome07.jpg" sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="323" alt="Welcome page"></p>
<ol start="5" sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="326">
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="326">On the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="326">Consistency check</strong> page, select <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="326">Consistency check</strong> to validate the conversion parameters.</li>
</ol>
<p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="328"><img src="media/consistency-check08.jpg" sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="328" alt="Consistency check translation setup page"></p>
<ol start="6" sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="330">
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="330">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="330">Consistency check</strong> dialog box, specify the details, and then select <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="330">OK</strong>.</li>
