<div class="NOTE" sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="332">
<h5>Note</h5>
<p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="333">If the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="333">Stop on the first error</strong> option on the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="333">Translation</strong> tab of the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="333">General ledger parameters</strong> page is set to <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="333">Yes</strong>, you can't move on to the next page of the wizard until the conversion parameters are checked for additional errors.</p>
</div>
<p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="335"><img src="media/consistency-check09.jpg" sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="335" alt="Consistency check page"></p>
