<p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="341"><img src="media/selection10.jpg" sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="341" alt="Selection page"></p>
