<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="344">On the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="344">Transaction processing</strong> page, select <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="344">Next</strong> to run the data conversion.</li>
