<p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="346"><img src="media/translation-processing11.jpg" sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-ledger-translation-procedure.md" sourcestartlinenumber="346" alt="Transaction processing page"></p>
